HEADWORD: Lubrical
<hw>Lu"bric*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>,
}</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>lubricus</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>lubrique</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Having a smooth surface;
slippery.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
